{"pageProps":{"frontmatter":{"title":"インサートモードから抜けたときに日本語入力モードから英字入力に自動で戻す(fcitx5)","description":"インサートモードから離れたときにfcitx5のコマンドを呼び出す","date":"2024-10-03","tag":["Linux","vim","InputMethod"]},"slug":"vim-leave-insert-fcitx5","innerHtml":"<h3 id=\"%E7%B5%90%E8%AB%96\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#%E7%B5%90%E8%AB%96\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> 結論</h3>\n<pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">augroup fcitx5_integration\n  <span class=\"token builtin\">autocmd</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">\" autocmd InsertEnter * :call system(</span><span class=\"token string\">'fcitx5-remote -o'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token builtin\">autocmd</span> InsertLeave <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">call</span> <span class=\"token function\">system</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'fcitx5-remote -c'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\naugroup END\n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> 環境</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>neovim 0.10.1</li>\n<li>fcitx5 5.1.10</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83%E6%96%87%E7%8C%AE\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83%E6%96%87%E7%8C%AE\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> 参考文献</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/keaising/im-select.nvim\">keaising/im-select.nvim: Switch Input Method automatically depends on Neovim's edit mode</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/brglng/vim-im-select\">brglng/vim-im-select: Improve Vim/Neovim experience with input methods.</a></li>\n</ul>\n","anchors":[{"text":"結論","link":"%E7%B5%90%E8%AB%96"},{"text":"環境","link":"%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83"},{"text":"参考文献","link":"%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83%E6%96%87%E7%8C%AE"}]},"__N_SSG":true}